  <description type="morphology">Roots  brown, in dense mass often covering stems.  Stem  scales black to dark brown, triangular-acuminate to lanceolate-acuminate, clathrate, papillate-ciliolate.  Leaves  erect-arching, 1--4.5 dm.  Petiole  less than 3.5 cm.  Blade  20 × 1.3 cm, leathery; base narrowly cuneate to attenuate; apex acute to rounded.  Sori  to 6 cm, ending ca. 0.5 cm below apex of blade. 2 n  = 74.</description>
